    "We tuned our models by adopting three variant learning rates (1e-5, 2e-5, 3e-5).",
    "The sequence length and batch size were set to 512 and 16, respectively.",
    "We processed all the textual content by removing non-Arabic text, special characters, URLs, diacritics, and emojis from the tweets.",
    "For STANCEOSAURUS, we extended the tweets with their context as suggested by the authors Zheng et al. (2022) who showed that extending the tweets with parent tweet text and/or embedded article titles can improve the performance of the stance models. 7",
